This is an excellent series of videos detailing some of the most inportant and influential architectural structures in the United States.  The way each video is layed out is very good, but as a series it is not an  exhaustive look at every significant home and architectural style in  America.  However, this is not the goal of this series.  It does, however,  give the viewer a glimpse into many significant residences in the United  States and a look at both the inside an outside of each.  A history of the  architect and proprietor is given, and information as to the location of  the home and its access to public is alos given.  Worth a look.
